<p>
  Dear <%= @tenant.name %>>,
</p>

<p>
  We would like to make you aware that your rental payments are now overdue.
  Here are payments information which are now overdue.
</p>

<table>
  <thead>
    <th>Property Name</th>
    <th>Landlord Name</th>
    <th>Due Date</th>
    <th>Amount</th>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <% @payments.each do |payment|%>
      <tr>
        <td><%= payment.property.name %></td>
        <td><%= payment.contract.landlord.name %></td>
        <td><%= payment.due_date.to_date %></td>
        <td><%= payment.precise_amount %></td>
      </tr>
    <% end %>
  </tbody>
</table>

<p>
  In case you were unaware, this payment can be made via PayPal, making payment a whole lot easier.
</p>

Regards,
